{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"ええ！\nハロハピの目標はもちろん、世界を笑顔にすることでしょう？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event217-14-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"でも、それだけじゃなくて、みんな新しい目標が\nできたと思うの！　それを言い合いましょう！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event217-14-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"はぐみ","body":"さんせー！\nはぐみはさっき薫くんが言ってくれたように、\n高校３年生を思いっきり楽しむのが目標だよ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event217-14-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"はぐみ","body":"あ！　あとはぐみ、もっと勉強をがんばりたい！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event217-14-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"はぐみ","body":"ひなちゃん先生に教えてもらっていろんなことがわかったら、\n勉強って楽しいかもって思ったんだ。\nだから、もっといろんなことを知ったら、もっと楽しくなるよね！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event217-14-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"はぐみ","body":"あ、もちろんスポーツも同じくらいがんばるよ！\n体育祭も最後だから、大活躍するんだっ！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event217-14-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薫","body":"はぐみ、その意気だよ。\nその気持ちは、必ず力になり実を結ぶはずさ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event217-14-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薫","body":"私は、そうだね……\n大学という新たな舞台に身を置くことになったわけだ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event217-14-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薫","body":"ブロードウェイへの留学経験も活かし、\n役者としてさらなる飛躍を果たしたいね","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event217-14-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"留学って、１週間の旅行のことかな？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"薫","body":"瀬田薫はこれからもより儚く……\nそして、より麗しい舞台のためにまい進すると誓うよ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event217-14-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"ふふっ、大学生になった薫さんのお芝居、楽しみだな～。\n……あ、えっと、次は私……かな……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"私は、薫さんやはぐみちゃんみたいにこれをがんばるって\nいうのはないんだけど……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"……自分から、友達を作りたいかな。\n声をかけられるのを待つだけじゃなくて、私から声をかけるの","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"それで、ハロハピのみんなが私に笑顔をくれたみたいに……\n私も、みんなに笑顔を届けられたらいいなって","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"……こ、こんなのが、目標じゃだめかな……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"いえ、そんなことないです。花音さんらしくていいと思います","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"……うん、ありがとう。\nそうしたら、美咲ちゃんの目標は？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"え、あたし？\nうーん……あんまり考えてなかったけど……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"……ま、なんだかんだで生徒会長になっちゃったんで。\nあたしにやれることをやるしかないかなって","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"あたし以外にとっても、高校生活の中の大事な１年間、\nみんなが楽しかったって思えるようにしたいというか……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"こころ","body":"ええ、美咲ならきっとできるわ！\n美咲が生徒会長の１年間、とっても楽しみだもの！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event217-14-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"けど、美咲ちゃんが生徒会長なんて、ほんとにすごいよね！\nどうしてやろうと思ったの？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event217-14-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"（ジャンケンで決まったなんて……絶対言えない……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event217-14-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"だからそれは……なんだかんだあって……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"